Masterchef Canada S01E08 - Major Steaks.

The home chefs are divided into 2 teams led by Kaila and Pino. The first challenge is to cook for 151 soldiers at CFB Trenton. The losing team has a pressure test featuring Salmon Wellington.

This episode originally aired on CTV on March 10, 2014. Like all of my releases to date, the source is an analog rip, so the quality is, at best, something like A8 V8.

There are several comments on TPB about the POKE release, saying that that file causes problems. This file should work fine on any system, though as I said above, the video and audio quality isn't going to win any awards.
